Package pt.uc.dei.entities

Class UserEntity

java.lang.Object
pt.uc.dei.entities.UserEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class UserEntity extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a system user with personal and account information.

Stores complete user profile including authentication details, roles, and organizational relationships. Managed through the user lifecycle from registration to deletion.
